{
  "texts": [
    "Lastly, the evaluation of APA (7th Edition) style citations and referencing in GPT-4 yielded mixed results.",
    "Out of the 16 citations provided, a majority (75%) referenced existing resources.",
    "However, errors were identified in some of the existing references, such as incorrect author names, missing DOIs, and incorrect links.",
    "Additionally, a notable portion (25%) of the citations pointed to non-existent references, including incorrect articles and broken links.",
    "The findings of this study highlight the ongoing challenges in leveraging AI language models like GPT-4 for scientific writing in school psychology."
  ]
}